    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "小道士",
        "李兴儿",
        "蔡天化",
        "贺仁杰"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李兴儿上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李兴儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是，待我上前叫门。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（小道士上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "小道士",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是李管家，到此何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李兴儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我奉了我家主母之命，要见老师父，有要紧的话说。"
        },
        {
          "character": "小道士",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "候着。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蔡天化上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡天化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "小道士",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李管家求见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡天化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唤他进来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "小道士",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我师父叫你哪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李兴儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贺仁杰暗上花墙。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李兴儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见老师父。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡天化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李兴儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老师父，大事不好了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡天化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何事惊慌？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李兴儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只因我家公子大爷，与你家大徒弟，在小东营，摆下百日擂台。打了九十多天，"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡天化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你等哪里知道：是我本月十九日夜晚，私入公衙，盗了赃官的印信。那赃官有"
        },
        {
          "character": "李兴儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既然如此，老师父，你老把这印信，要收好了才是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡天化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无妨。此物吾藏在玄天大帝兜裆之内，就是孔明复生，也难知晓。李管家，随"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蔡天化、李兴儿、小道士同下。贺仁杰下花墙。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺仁杰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀好呀，听他之言，此乃是天助俺成功也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贺仁杰盗印。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺仁杰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且喜印信到手，待我到大树林内，等候众家叔父便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贺仁杰下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "李兴儿→小道士",
          "turns": 2
        },
