    {
      "scene_index": 7,
      "label": "第七场",
      "characters_present": [
        "关泰",
        "蔡天化",
        "贺仁杰",
        "黄天霸"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄天霸、关泰、李堃、朱光祖、金大力同上，贺仁杰上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺仁杰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见众位叔父。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "印信之事如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺仁杰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "印信已被小侄盗来，叔父请看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好。一同带路前往。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同走圆场。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺仁杰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，蔡天化可在里面？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蔡天化、众徒弟同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡天化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "徒弟们打座！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蔡天化上台。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，月台之上，坐的敢是蔡天化？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡天化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你祖师号悟清。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蔡天化，你私盗皇家国宝，该当何罪？今特带领人来，与尔要印。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡天化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住了！印信既被你等盗回，休得在你祖师爷跟前卖弄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺仁杰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蔡天化，前番盗印，不足为奇，二次被你少爷盗回，方显手段。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡天化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀，小小年纪，口出朗言大话，通尔的名来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺仁杰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你少爷住江南金华县四霸天贺天保之子贺仁杰！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡天化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "晚生下辈，何足道哉。那一个红脸的呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你老爷，家住山西蒲州府，漕标参将，姓关名泰，字小西！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡天化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无名之辈，也不在你祖师爷的心上，闪开！那一白面，他是何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你且听了！你老爷家住江南绍兴府金华县，飞镖黄三泰之子，四霸天赛罗成黄"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天霸！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡天化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵，呀呀呀呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看镖！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡天化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "久闻你黄家金镖厉害，每每伤害绿林，今日一见也是平常。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡天化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众徒弟一齐动手！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蔡天化下高台，亮相，起打。贺仁杰使流星打蔡天化，蔡天化下，众徒弟同下。众人同追下。蔡天化上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡天化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住。那一娃娃，手中不知使的什么兵刃，耀人二目，打了我这啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡天化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众徒弟走上。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众徒弟同上。黄天霸、关泰、李堃、朱光祖、金大力、贺仁杰同上，开打，打连环。金大力擒蔡天化。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡天化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无量寿佛。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
